{
  "texts": [
    "We randomly select 500 samples from our training set and we feed the model with an instruction prompt.",
    "We compare the generated ABC notations with the ground truth.",
    "The fraction of examples where the generated and ground truth tokens are identical for the entire sequence is 0.02%.",
    "Furthermore, partial matches occur in 0.24% of the training examples, where the generated and ground truth sequences share at least 80% of their tokens.",
    "In conclusion, our study introduces ChatMusician, an innovative open-source LLM capable of advanced music reasoning and composition."
  ]
}